&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/EUR-MUNICH-TANTRIS-OFFER-LOGO-MEDIUM.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-4343&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/EUR-MUNICH-TANTRIS-OFFER-LOGO-MEDIUM.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;EUR- MUNICH- TANTRIS- OFFER- LOGO MEDIUM&quot; width=&quot;75&quot; height=&quot;75&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.elitetraveler.com/finest-dining/top-100-restaurants-in-the-world/tantris&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-3918&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/MEDIA-ELITE-TRAVELER-LOGO1.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;MEDIA- ELITE TRAVELER LOGO1&quot; width=&quot;80&quot; height=&quot;80&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.gayot.com/restaurants/tantris-munich-80805-bavaria-germany_135ge080501.html&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-5445&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/MEDIA-GAYOT-LOGO-SMALL1.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;MEDIA- GAYOT LOGO SMALL&quot; width=&quot;100&quot; height=&quot;64&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;While seated in the retro Asian-inspired dining room, experience the cooking of chef Hans Haas. His nouvelle European cuisine with an exotic twist has garnered&lt;strong&gt; 2 Michelin stars&lt;/strong&gt;, a &lt;strong&gt;Gayot rating of 19/20,&nbsp;# 65 of&nbsp;The Elite 100&lt;/strong&gt;&nbsp;and &lt;strong&gt;#86 on the World&rsquo;s 50 Best Restaurants 2013&lt;/strong&gt; list. Dressy attire; jacket preferred for gentlemen.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please &lt;a title=&quot;Tantris Reservations&quot; href=&quot;http://www.tantris.de/reservations.php&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;book online&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;or contact Tantris by phone at +49.89.361.9590 or email at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:info@tantris.de&quot;&gt;info@tantris.de&lt;/a&gt; to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time and either a cell phone number or a local number in Munich (hotel) where the restaurant can reach you if necessary. Also provide any details if this is a special occasion or if there are allergies for any of the guests dining.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant Tantris requires a credit card to hold your reservation. Your credit card will not be charged at the time of booking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cancellation and/or amendment of a&nbsp;dinner&lt;strong&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;reservation is free of charge until 12:00 noon on the reserved date and for a&nbsp;lunch&nbsp;reservation until 9:00 am on the reserved date.&nbsp;In the event of non-attendance, a late amendment or late cancellation, Tantris reserves the right to charge a penalty fee of &euro; 100 per person.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Please contact the restaurant by phone at +49.89.361.9590 or email at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:info@tantris.de&quot;&gt;info@tantris.de&lt;/a&gt; 24 hours prior to your dining date to reconfirm. Provide your booking confirmation number and a reminder that this is a Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection reservation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based on availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A main course must be purchased to receive your dining benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

